Tune in to the new @thedispatch podcast to hear our fact checking team break down some of the most common viral falsehoods of the past week. And to hear me inadvertently insult my mother's pumpkin pie, which is actually very good! (Sorry, Mom.)
https://t.co/0mmApmlvvs
text.1: Viral videos claim to show PA poll workers filling out blank ballots. According to officials, they were transcribing votes from damaged ballots onto clean ones. Unedited videos show bipartisan observers present the whole time. A fact check for @thedispatch:https://t.co/gbf8xdWgc4
text.2:
The Dispatch fact-checkers had a very busy week -- responding in realtime to many of the conspiracies and false claims about the election and its aftermath. So we invited them on the podcast to discuss their work. W/@Alec_Dent, @KhayaHimmelman & @EggerDC
